ADM begins $ 80 mln lysine plant expansion . Archer Daniels Midland Co said Wednesday it has begun an $ 80 million expansion of its Decatur , Illinois , lysine plant . Once the expansion is completed , the facility , ADM ' s only lysine plant , will have a total annual capacity of 350 million pounds , the company said . " This expansion is in response to the rapidly growing worldwide market for high quality feed additives , " ADM said in a release . Further information on the company ' s current lysine production capacity was not immediately available . ( ( - - Chicago newsdesk , 312 - 408 - 8787 ) ) 
